Class Parser

  • java.lang.Object
    • myn.notifi.protocol.Parser

  • public class Parser
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides basic functions for converting big-Endian to little endian Convert int, short, double from big endian to little endian and the corresponding read/write functions
